MARKET_INFO.1UP: 1UP will reward you earlier if your team takes a one-goal lead, e.g. 1-0, 0-1, 2-1, 1-2, 3-2, 2-3. Once settled, the final result no longer matters - win, lose or draw! Betting on the draw in this market is the same as in regular 1X2, it is resulted on the full-time score regardless of how and when any goals are scored (which is why the odds are the same).
MARKET_INFO.2UP: 2UP will reward you earlier if your team takes a two-goal lead, e.g. 2-0, 0-2, 3-1, 1-3, 4-2, 2-4. Once settled, the final result no longer matters - win, lose or draw! If a match is abandoned and a team has gone two or more goals ahead then bets on that selection will still be paid as winners. Aradabet reserves the right to void bets/selections if we identify any suspected illegal activity, bonus abuse, or violations of our terms and conditions.
